title: The Anna Kendrick Proposal Mixtape [24bit FLAC] vinyl
description:
The Anna Kendrick Proposal Mixtape [24bit FLAC] vinyl

  Source: vinyl
  Codec: FLAC
  Bit Rate: ~ 2,500 kbps
  Bit Depth: 24
  Sample Rate: 88 kHz - 96 kHz

  01 There is a Light That Never Goes Out - The Smiths
  02 Lovesong - The Cure
  03 So Far Away - Carole King
  04 Hard Headed Woman - Cat Stevens
  05 Body and Soul - Billie Holiday
  06 For My Lover - Tracy Chapman
  07 My Heart - Paramore
  08 I'm Your Man - Leonard Cohen
  09 Something in the Way She Moves - James Taylor
  10 Hallelujah - Jeff Buckley
  11 Heart of Gold - Neil Young 
  12 Sexy Boy - Air
  13 I Still Do - The Cranberries

  This is an old fashioned 1990s mixtape comprised of thirteen 24bit vinyl-ripped FLAC tracks.  It is dedicated to one of the shining lights of our generation.  Anna Kendrick is a gifted actress, yet she is as modest as she is beautiful.  Full of talent, wit and irony, she is someone who doesn't come along every day.  I made this as a tribute to her good taste.  Patiently waiting for Pitch Perfect 2.
